  "title": "🔥Brand Sales Representative (Entry-Level)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Fixed Working Hours | Training Provided | No Experience Required</strong></p><p>We are looking for motivated individuals to join our team as a Brand Sales Representative. In this role, you will represent assigned brands, engage with customers, and develop practical sales and communication skills. No prior experience is required, as full training and mentorship will be provided.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Represent and promote brands to generate sales</p></li><li><p>Engage customers professionally and build positive brand experiences</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Open to entry-level candidates with no prior experience</p></li><li><p>Fresh graduates and ORD personnel are welcome</p></li></ul><p><strong>What We Offer:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Fixed working hours</p></li><li><p>Structured training and mentorship</p></li><li><p>Supportive team environment</p></li><li><p>Career development and progression opportunities</p></li></ul><p>If you are eager to learn and grow in a sales-oriented role, we encourage you to apply.</p><p>📩 <strong>Apply now to begin your career journey with us.</strong></p>",
